<div id="pf28" class="pf w8 h3" data-page-no="28"><div class="pc pc28 w8 h3"><img class="bi x0 y0 w9 h4" alt="" src="bg28.png"/><div class="t m1e x45 h22 y535 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">given for the benefit of the church as a whole, not merely to benefit the </div><div class="t m41e x45 h22 y536 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">individual. No one person has every gift. (See 1 Cor. 12:27-31.) Paul de-</div><div class="t m41f x45 h22 y571 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">clares that he would rather speak five words with understanding than ten </div><div class="t m77 x45 h22 y538 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thousand words in an unknown tongue. (See 1 Cor. 14:19.). </div><div class="t m420 x45 h21 y8 ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m29 x30 h22 y8 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Please summarize this lesson in your own words: </div><div class="t m421 x2a h21 y3bf ff6 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">APPLICATION </div><div class="t md8 x63 h22 y3c0 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Am I walking after the flesh or after the Spirit? </div><div class="t m422 x63 h22 y3c2 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Do I pray earnestly daily for the power of the Spirit to possess my </div><div class="t m37e x63 h22 y3c4 ff5 fsf fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">life and to use me in God&apos;s work? </div><div class="t m423 x32 h4d y572 ff6 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What Happened to Our </div><div class="t m1df x6a h4d y25b ff6 fs23 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible Book Studies? </div><div class="t m424 x32 h32 y573 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Bible book curriculum has been in-</div><div class="t m425 x32 h32 y574 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">terrupted in order to make it possible </div><div class="t m426 x32 h32 y575 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">for the world church to review the </div><div class="t m427 xad h34 y576 ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">27 </div><div class="t m428 x32 h32 y577 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">fundamental beliefs of Seventh-day </div><div class="t m429 x32 h32 y578 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Adventists. We resume our study of the </div><div class="t m42a x32 h32 y579 ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Bible books beginning with the first </div><div class="t me2 x32 h32 y50e ff5 fs15 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">quarter of </div><div class="t m42b x4e h34 y50e ff5 fs16 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1989. </div><div class="t m161 x45 h23 y2da ff6 fs10 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">40 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
